After the user has shaped twenty five moments, completed playback, and either accepted or declined protection, they enter the first real use of their preserved voice.

First Message Creation is the moment the user experiences ESSENCE as a tool, not just a ceremony. It must feel warm, guided, simple, and emotionally supportive.

