### 13.1 Purpose of the First Message Flow

This flow must:

Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ introduce users to message creation in an easy way
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ help them choose who the message is for
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ offer gentle structure through templates
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ give them emotional confidence
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ create a message that feels personal and heartfelt
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ give a cinematic reveal of a generated message
